measure.CatchLine: Allows land division to separate dwelling units for new middle housing allowed in cities.
measure.MeasureSummary: Allows land division to separate dwelling units for new middle housing allowed in cities. Applies to divisions permitted on or after July 1, 2022. Prohibits homeowners associations or restrictive covenants from forbidding partition. Delays applicability of limits on private middle housing restrictions.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to land division for residential development.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to land division for residential development.
measure.AtTheRequestOf: (at the request of Habitat for Humanity)
